metadata.name: The Mirror
metadata.description:
The girl took off all her clothes and stood naked in the mirror. Every second the cold air licked her skin, she got sharp goosebumps. But her own beautiful body and face in the mirror made the goosebumps erotically pleasant. 
The girl drew close to the mirror and whispered, "Mirror, mirror on the wall, whoâ€™s the fairest of them all?"
Then the mirror answered, "Stay away from the truth."
